.org/resource/Aircoach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plane\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were all dumbfounded,\\\" Mr Duggan said.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Duggan\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the guys said 'Kieran has room in the car' and I said 'yeah, I can fit three or four of you in if you want to jump in'.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\", \"score\": 0.9694439945508538, \"rank\": 0.0315169990549953, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Mitchell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"room\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the car\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What was more surprising was his reaction - he said 'yeah I might take you up on that'.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his reaction\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They left the plane first and we walked out after that.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plane\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we got to the baggage hall I could not see any of the guys so we walked out through arrivals ...\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the baggage hall\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"arrivals\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said to one of the guys that maybe I'd better stay on because Fintan sounded quite genuine.\\\"\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"e